OL,3,CJoiner dragged along road by car
OL,4,Cdriven by thieves stealing his tools
OL,6,FA joiner was dragged along the road by
OL,7,Fa car driven by thieves who had stolen
OL,8,Fhis tools.
OL,10,FLuke Yardley, 33, was working at a
OL,11,Fhouse on Rosehill Road in Burnley when
OL,12,Fhe caught a gang of men stealing tools
OL,13,Ffrom his van after he was alerted by a
OL,14,Floud bang.
OL,16,FHe raced towards the gang as they
OL,17,Fpacked his equipment into a black
OL,18,FVolkswagen Golf, and tried to grab his
OL,19,FDewalt tool bag through a window when
OL,20,Fthe car sped off.
