OL,3,CJoiner dragged along road by car
OL,4,Cdriven by thieves stealing his tools
OL,6,F"I've got four children under the age
OL,7,Fof five and have a family to support.
OL,8,FI've had to buy new tools but have had
OL,9,Fto take a few days off and I just hope
OL,10,Fthat I can make that up quickly
OL,11,Fthrough getting more jobs and working
OL,12,Fovertime."
OL,14,FThe items stolen, worth around #1,000
OL,15,Fin total, included an 18V Dewalt
OL,16,Fmultitool, an 18V Dewalt orbital
OL,17,FSander, a Dewalt laser level, an 18V
OL,18,FBosch SDS drill, an 18V Dewalt combi
OL,19,Fdrill, four 18V Dewalt batteries, a
OL,20,FDewalt powertool bag and a Dewalt Leaf
OL,21,FBlower.
