OL,4,Cdriven by thieves stealing his tools
OL,6,FLuke has passed on descriptions of the
OL,7,Fmen inside the Golf to police and the
OL,8,FLancashire Force has confirmed they
OL,9,Fare looking into it.
OL,11,FThey are obtaining doorbell camera
OL,12,Ffootage from nearby houses and several
OL,13,Fnames have been forwarded to officers,
OL,14,Fwho are appealing for information.
